             were indicted for <rs id="t18240603-240-off1244" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18240603-240-off1244" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18240603-240-off1244" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the 31st of May, seven shillings and three sixpences
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18240603-240-victim2052" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Welch
                  <interp inst="t18240603-240-victim2052" type="surname" value="Welch"></interp>
